  "prompt": "What do the lyrics to \"Tunak Tunak Tun\" mean in English?",
  "response": "\"Tunak Tunak Tun\" is a popular Punjabi song by Indian artist Daler Mehndi. The song's lyrics do not have a deep or complex meaning; they are mostly playful and celebratory. Here's a rough translation of the chorus from Punjabi to English:\n\n\"Tunak Tunak Tun, Tunak Tunak Tun, Tunak Tunak Tun, Da Da Da.\"\n\nThe lyrics are largely nonsensical and are intended to be catchy and rhythmic rather than conveying a specific message. The song is known for its infectious beat and energetic dance movements. It\u2019s mainly about having fun and enjoying the music.",
